{"tha-ap474:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap474:0.2":"Nalamalivagga ","tha-ap474:0.3":"Manipujakattheraapadana ","tha-ap474:1.1":"“Padumuttaro nama jino, ","tha-ap474:1.2":"sabbadhammana paragu; ","tha-ap474:1.3":"Vivekakamo sambuddho, ","tha-ap474:1.4":"gacchate anilanjase. ","tha-ap474:2.1":"Avidure himavantassa, ","tha-ap474:2.2":"mahajatassaro ahu; ","tha-ap474:2.3":"Tattha me bhavanam asi, ","tha-ap474:2.4":"punnakammena samyutam. ","tha-ap474:3.1":"Bhavana abhinikkhamma, ","tha-ap474:3.2":"addasam lokanayakam; ","tha-ap474:3.3":"Indivaramva jalitam, ","tha-ap474:3.4":"adittamva hutasanam. ","tha-ap474:4.1":"Vicinam naddasam puppham, ","tha-ap474:4.2":"pujayissanti nayakam; ","tha-ap474:4.3":"Sakam cittam pasadetva, ","tha-ap474:4.4":"avandim satthuno aham. ","tha-ap474:5.1":"Mama sise manim gayha, ","tha-ap474:5.2":"pujayim lokanayakam; ","tha-ap474:5.3":"Imaya manipujaya, ","tha-ap474:5.4":"vipako hotu bhaddako. ","tha-ap474:6.1":"Padumuttaro lokavidu, ","tha-ap474:6.2":"ahutinam patiggaho; ","tha-ap474:6.3":"Antalikkhe thito sattha, ","tha-ap474:6.4":"imam gatham abhasatha. ","tha-ap474:7.1":"‘So te ijjhatu sankappo, ","tha-ap474:7.2":"labhassu vipulam sukham; ","tha-ap474:7.3":"Imaya manipujaya, ","tha-ap474:7.4":"anubhohi mahayasam’. ","tha-ap474:8.1":"Idam vatvana bhagava, ","tha-ap474:8.2":"jalajuttamanamako; ","tha-ap474:8.3":"Agamasi buddhasettho, ","tha-ap474:8.4":"yattha cittam panihitam. ","tha-ap474:9.1":"Satthikappani devindo, ","tha-ap474:9.2":"devarajjamakarayim; ","tha-ap474:9.3":"Anekasatakkhattunca, ","tha-ap474:9.4":"cakkavatti ahosaham. ","tha-ap474:10.1":"Pubbakammam sarantassa, ","tha-ap474:10.2":"devabhutassa me sato; ","tha-ap474:10.3":"Mani nibbattate mayham, ","tha-ap474:10.4":"alokakarano mamam. ","tha-ap474:11.1":"Chalasitisahassani, ","tha-ap474:11.2":"nariyo me pariggaha; ","tha-ap474:11.3":"Vicittavatthabharana, ","tha-ap474:11.4":"amukkamanikundala. ","tha-ap474:12.1":"Alarapamha hasula, ","tha-ap474:12.2":"susanna tanumajjhima; ","tha-ap474:12.3":"Parivarenti mam niccam, ","tha-ap474:12.4":"manipujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap474:13.1":"Sonnamaya manimaya, ","tha-ap474:13.2":"lohitangamaya tatha; ","tha-ap474:13.3":"Bhanda me sukata honti, ","tha-ap474:13.4":"yadicchasi pilandhana. ","tha-ap474:14.1":"Kutagara gaharamma, ","tha-ap474:14.2":"sayananca maharaham; ","tha-ap474:14.3":"Mama sankappamannaya, ","tha-ap474:14.4":"nibbattanti yadicchakam. ","tha-ap474:15.1":"Labha tesam suladdhanca, ","tha-ap474:15.2":"ye labhanti upassutim; ","tha-ap474:15.3":"Punnakkhettam manussanam, ","tha-ap474:15.4":"osadham sabbapaninam. ","tha-ap474:16.1":"Mayhampi sukatam kammam, ","tha-ap474:16.2":"yoham adakkhi nayakam; ","tha-ap474:16.3":"Vinipata pamuttomhi, ","tha-ap474:16.4":"pattomhi acalam padam. ","tha-ap474:17.1":"Yam yam yonupapajjami, ","tha-ap474:17.2":"devattam atha manusam; ","tha-ap474:17.3":"Divasanceva rattinca, ","tha-ap474:17.4":"aloko hoti me sada. ","tha-ap474:18.1":"Tayeva manipujaya, ","tha-ap474:18.2":"anubhotvana sampada; ","tha-ap474:18.3":"Nanaloko maya dittho, ","tha-ap474:18.4":"pattomhi acalam padam. ","tha-ap474:19.1":"Satasahassito kappe, ","tha-ap474:19.2":"yam manim abhipujayim; ","tha-ap474:19.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap474:19.4":"manipujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap474:20.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap474:20.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap474:20.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap474:21.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap474:21.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap474:21.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap474:22.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap474:22.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap474:22.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap474:23.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma manipujako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap474:24.1":"Manipujakattherassapadanam dutiyam. "}